<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <%- include('./head'); %>
  </head>

  <body class="bg-dark text-white">
    <header><%- include('./header'); %></header>

    <main class="container py-5 text-center">
      <div><%- include('./tabs'); %></div>

      <section class="bg-secondary bg-gradient p-5 rounded shadow mb-5">
        <h2 class="mb-4">Develop Your Solutions with Student Team</h2>
        <p>
          Work-life orientation is reflected in our teaching through various
          types of student projects. These projects provide employers with an
          excellent opportunity to engage our skilled and enthusiastic students.
          The outcomes of these projects deliver solutions and ideas for the
          specific practical problem you define, whether it involves marketing
          planning or product development.
        </p>
        <p>
          The scope of work, scheduling, and implementation methods are always
          tailored collaboratively to meet the situation's needs.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-5">
        <h3 class="mb-3">Propose a Project Topic and Gain</h3>
        <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
          <li class="list-group-item bg-dark text-white">
            Fresh perspectives and development ideas to solve your challenges
          </li>
          <li class="list-group-item bg-dark text-white">
            The latest research insights to enhance your operations
          </li>
          <li class="list-group-item bg-dark text-white">
            Access to our modern learning and service environments
          </li>
          <li class="list-group-item bg-dark text-white">
            Positive visibility and an opportunity to introduce your company to
            potential future employees
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-5">
        <h3 class="mb-3">Project Workflow</h3>
        <div class="row g-4 text-start">
          <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
            <div class="card h-100 bg-dark text-white">
              <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">1. Define the Project Content</h5>
                <ul>
                  <li>What practical problem do you need solutions for?</li>
                  <li>What kind of expertise do you require?</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
            <div class="card h-100 bg-dark text-white">
              <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">2. Get in Touch</h5>
                <p>
                  Email:
                  <a href="mailto:palvelut@karelia.fi" class="link-primary"
                    >palvelut@karelia.fi</a
                  >
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
            <div class="card h-100 bg-dark text-white">
              <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">3. Agree on Implementation</h5>
                <p>
                  We will determine the scope, schedule, and approach together.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-6">
            <div class="card h-100 bg-dark text-white">
              <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">4. Students Execute the Project</h5>
                <p>
                  Under instructor guidance. Interim meetings involving the
                  client can be arranged as needed.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-6">
            <div class="card h-100 bg-dark text-white">
              <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">5. Presentation of Results</h5>
                <p>
                  You are warmly invited to attend and provide feedback on the
                  presentations!
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-5">
        <h3 class="mb-3">Duration and Timing</h3>
        <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
          <li class="list-group-item bg-dark text-white">
            Varies by case, ranging from 1–2 days to an entire semester.
          </li>
          <li class="list-group-item bg-dark text-white">
            Project proposals can be submitted year-round.
          </li>
          <li class="list-group-item bg-dark text-white">
            Implementation takes place in the following semester (e.g., proposal
            in autumn → execution in spring).
          </li>
          <li class="list-group-item bg-dark text-white">
            Projects are integrated into specific study modules.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-5">
        <h3 class="mb-3">What is Expected from the Client?</h3>
        <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
          <li class="list-group-item bg-dark text-white">
            Requirements depend on the project's scope.
          </li>
          <li class="list-group-item bg-dark text-white">
            Participation in meetings with students and university
            representatives as needed.
          </li>
          <li class="list-group-item bg-dark text-white">
            Providing information and communication to support project
            execution.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>
    </main>

    <footer><%- include('./footer'); %></footer>
  </body>
</html>
